{
  "number": 57,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/57",
  "title": "Components organisation",
  "body": "Right now we have:\n\n![2015-09-03-140553_262x457_scrot](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/123822/9657846/f8ff021e-5244-11e5-96d7-ff6768353717.png)\n\nIt always feels to me too much folders, don't you think we could flatten this like:\n- BemHelper.js\n- Hits.js\n- MultipleChoiceList.js\n- Pagination.js\n- PaginationHiddenLink.js\n- PaginationLink.js\n- Paginator.js\n- Searchbox.js\n- Template.js\n\nSo that we remove lot of folders and do not have that much of index.js files.\n\nIf at some point a component needs external files, then we can make a folder for this case.\n",
